tras/49a2b9ab349b5b3c627e4053bfece0db.webm?t=1727877368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057430/extras/49a2b9ab349b5b3c627e4053bfece0db.mp4?t=1727877368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Features:<br><br>1) Colorful and stunning space views<br>2) Various enemies<br>3) Several types of weapons<br>4) Spaceship with controls like in flight simulators<br>5) 6 interesting missions<br>6) Mesmerizing soundtrack",
